export const homeObjOne = {
    lightBg: false, 
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: 'Exclusive Access',
    headLine: 'Unlimited Transactions with zero fees',
    description: 'Get access to our excclusive diamond card that allows you to send unlimited transaction without getting charged any fees',
    buttonLabel: 'Get Started',
    imgStart: '',
    img: 'images/svg-1.svg',
    alt: 'Credit Card'
};

export const homeObjTwo = {
  lightBg: true, 
  lightText: false,
  lightTextDesc: false,
  topLine: 'Hello There,',
  headLine: 'I\'m Javier.',
  description: 'UI/UX Designer and Front-End Developer currently based in Salinas, CA. ',
  buttonLabel: 'View Portfolio',
  imgStart: '',
  img: 'images/portrait.png',
  alt: 'portrait'
};

  
export const homeObjFour = {
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: 'DATA ANALYTICS',
    headline: 'Every transaction is stored on our secure cloud database',
    description:
      'Never ever have to worry again about saved reciepts. We store your data, so you can access it anytime.',
    buttonLabel: 'Sign Up Now',
    imgStart: 'start',
    img: 'images/svg-8.svg',
    alt: 'Vault'
};


export const gridObj = {
  img1: 'images/svg-1.svg',
  img2: 'images/svg-2.svg',
  img3: 'images/svg-3.svg',
  img4: 'images/svg-4.svg',

};
